<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.10.5">
<l>kuṭaiyā varaiyāl niraimuṉ kātta perumāṉ maruvāta</l>
<l>viṭaitā ṉēḻum veṉṟāṉ kōval niṉṟāṉ teṉṉilaṅkai</l>
<l>yaṭaiyā varakkar vīyap porutu mēvi veṅkūṟṟam</l>
<l>naṭaiyā vuṇṇak kaṇṭāṉ nāmam namōnā rāyaṇamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The name of the great lord who, long ago, protected the herd</l>
<l rend="indent">with a mountain as an umbrella,</l>
<l>The one who conquered seven inimical bulls, the one who stands in Kōvalūr,</l>
<l>The one who, joining the fighting so the impious demons</l>
<l rend="indent">in Laṅkā of the South perished,</l>
<l>Saw that cruel Death devoured them quickly,</l>
<l rend="indent">[that itself is] the Namō Nārāyaṇam.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
